    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-103@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The `.klz` parcel: move work without a server"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "`.klz`-pakken: flytt arbeid uten server"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-104@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A `.klz` is a portable, single-file carrier — the way you hand work between\nmachines or people without a server. It comes in two profiles:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En `.klz` er en portabel bærer i én fil — måten du leverer arbeid mellom maskiner\neller personer på uten en server. Den finnes i to profiler:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-105@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Source travels as identity + a round-trip skeleton by default; add `--with-source`\nto embed the raw originals (for offline re-extraction)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kilden reiser som identitet + et rundtur-skjelett som standard; legg til `--with-source`\nfor å bygge inn de rå originalene (for frakoblet re-uttrekk)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-106@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Do ad-hoc and project mode mix?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kan ad hoc og prosjektmodus kombineres?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-107@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Yes — because they're the same commands over different bindings, not rival\ntoolsets. The guidance:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ja — fordi de er de samme kommandoene over ulike bindinger, ikke rivaliserende\nverktøysett. Rettesnoren:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-108@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Coherent mixes:** a tool run *inside* a project (`kapi ai-translate src/app.json`)\nstill picks up the project's defaults and TM while working on a single file; the\nsame flow runs ad-hoc or process-only with no change; a `.klz` made in a project\nis consumed ad-hoc by a reviewer and `merge`d back."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Kombinasjoner som henger sammen:** et verktøy kjørt *inne i* et prosjekt (`kapi ai-translate src/app.json`)\nplukker fortsatt opp prosjektets standardvalg og oversettelsesminne mens det\narbeider på én enkelt fil; den samme flyten kjører ad hoc eller med ren\nprosessering uten endring; en `.klz` laget i et prosjekt brukes ad hoc av en\nkorrekturleser og flettes tilbake med `merge`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-109@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**The one thing to avoid:** running **two stateful stores over the same content** —\nan ad-hoc `.klz` workspace *and* a `.kapi` project for the same files. Use the\n`.klz` workspace when there is no project; use the project store when there is."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Det ene du bør unngå:** å kjøre **to tilstandsfulle lagre over samme innhold** —\net ad hoc `.klz`-arbeidsområde *og* et `.kapi`-prosjekt for de samme filene. Bruk\n`.klz`-arbeidsområdet når det ikke finnes noe prosjekt; bruk prosjektlageret når\ndet gjør det."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-10@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Prefer a visual interface? [Kapi Desktop](/kapi/desktop/overview) wraps the same\ntools and flows in a native app with a flow editor, live runner, plugin manager,\nand credential vault. The [Kapi Desktop overview](/kapi/desktop/overview) walks\nthrough your first project."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Foretrekker du et visuelt grensesnitt? [Kapi Desktop](/kapi/desktop/overview)\npakker de samme verktøyene og flytene inn i en app med flytredigering,\nkjøringsvisning, tilleggshåndtering og legitimasjonshvelv.\n[Kapi Desktop-oversikten](/kapi/desktop/overview) tar deg gjennom ditt første\nprosjekt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-110@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Worth knowing:** inside a project, an explicit `-o` writes a file and skips the\nstore (process-only) — that's intentional, and `--explain` shows you which you got."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Verdt å vite:** inne i et prosjekt skriver en eksplisitt `-o` en fil og hopper\nover lageret (ren prosessering) — det er tilsiktet, og `--explain` viser deg\nhvilken du fikk."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
