    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-155@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Create your first project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Opprett ditt første prosjekt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-156@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The [Quick Start](/kapi/get-started/quickstart) runs kapi ad-hoc — one command,\none file, flags for everything. That's the right shape for a one-off. For content\nyou localize **more than once** — a repository, a product's strings, a docs set —\na **`.kapi` project** is the working model worth adopting: you capture the\nlanguages, content patterns, and flows in a committed recipe once, then drive\neverything through short commands with no repeated flags."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "[Hurtigstarten](/kapi/get-started/quickstart) kjører kapi ad hoc — én kommando,\nén fil, flagg for alt. Det er riktig form for et engangstilfelle. For innhold du\nlokaliserer **mer enn én gang** — et kodelager, et produkts strenger, et\ndokumentasjonssett — er et **`.kapi`-prosjekt** arbeidsmodellen verdt å ta i\nbruk: du fanger språkene, innholdsmønstrene og flytene i en innsjekket oppskrift\nén gang, og driver deretter alt gjennom korte kommandoer uten gjentatte flagg."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-157@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "This page walks the smallest end-to-end loop: `init` → read the recipe → run a\nflow → `merge` the files out."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Denne siden går gjennom den minste ende-til-ende-sløyfen: `init` → les\noppskriften → kjør en flyt → `merge` filene ut."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-158@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "1. Initialize the project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "1. Initialiser prosjektet"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-159@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Run `kapi init` in the directory you want to localize. It scaffolds a\n`<dir-name>.kapi` recipe and an adjacent `.kapi/` state directory:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Kjør `kapi init` i katalogen du vil lokalisere. Den setter opp en\n`<dir-name>.kapi`-oppskrift og en tilstøtende `.kapi/`-tilstandskatalog:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-15@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Kapi finds your project automatically.** Like git, it walks up the directory\ntree from wherever you run it; if it finds a `.kapi` recipe, it runs in\n**project mode** with that project's languages, defaults, and flows. Otherwise\nit runs ad-hoc."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Kapi finner prosjektet ditt automatisk.** Som git går den oppover i\nkatalogtreet fra der du kjører den; finner den en `.kapi`-oppskrift, kjører den\ni **prosjektmodus** med prosjektets språk, standardvalg og flyter. Ellers kjører\nden ad hoc."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-160@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The recipe is committed; the `.kapi/` state directory is regenerable and belongs\nin `.gitignore`. A fresh `init` declares your languages but **no content yet** —\nthat's the next step."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oppskriften sjekkes inn; `.kapi/`-tilstandskatalogen kan regenereres og hører\nhjemme i `.gitignore`. En fersk `init` oppgir språkene dine, men **ennå ikke noe\ninnhold** — det er neste steg."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-161@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "2. Declare the content to localize"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "2. Oppgi innholdet som skal lokaliseres"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-162@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Tell the project which files to translate with `kapi add` — a glob, plus the\nformat (auto-detected if you omit it):"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Fortell prosjektet hvilke filer som skal oversettes med `kapi add` — et\nglobmønster, pluss formatet (auto-oppdaget hvis du utelater det):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-163@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Each `kapi add` appends a content entry to the recipe; `kapi rm` removes one and\n`kapi ls` lists the files the project currently tracks (add `--stats` for per-file\nblock and word counts):"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver `kapi add` legger til en innholdsoppføring i oppskriften; `kapi rm` fjerner\nén og `kapi ls` lister filene prosjektet for øyeblikket sporer (legg til\n`--stats` for blokk- og ordtellinger per fil):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-164@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "If your strings live in a known stack's i18n catalogs, skip the manual `add` and\nlet `kapi init --framework <stack>` (for example `react-i18next`, `nextjs`,\n`flutter`) pre-fill the content mapping for you — see\n`kapi presets list --framework`."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hvis strengene dine ligger i i18n-katalogene til en kjent teknologistabel, hopp\nover den manuelle `add`-en og la `kapi init --framework <stack>` (for eksempel\n`react-i18next`, `nextjs`, `flutter`) forhåndsutfylle innholdskartleggingen for\ndeg — se `kapi presets list --framework`."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-165@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "3. Read the recipe"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "3. Les oppskriften"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-166@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The `<dir-name>.kapi` recipe is a portable YAML document. A minimal one declares\nits languages, the content globs to localize, and the flows to run:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "`<dir-name>.kapi`-oppskriften er et portabelt YAML-dokument. En minimal en\noppgir språkene sine, innholdsglobene som skal lokaliseres, og flytene som skal\nkjøres:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-167@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "`kapi add` wrote the `content` entry's source `path` and `format`. The optional\n`target` glob — with the `{lang}` placeholder — tells `merge` where each locale's\nfiles go; set it for a custom layout (or let `--framework` fill it), otherwise\nkapi defaults to a locale-suffixed path beside the source. `defaults` carries the\nsource and target languages every command inherits, and `flows` names reusable\ntool chains. See the [project file reference](/reference/project-file) for the\nfull schema."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "`kapi add` skrev innholdsoppføringens kilde-`path` og `format`. Den valgfrie\n`target`-globen — med `{lang}`-plassholderen — forteller `merge` hvor hvert\nspråks filer går; sett den for en tilpasset struktur (eller la `--framework`\nfylle den), ellers bruker kapi som standard en språkkode-suffiksert sti ved siden\nav kilden. `defaults` bærer kilde- og målspråkene hver kommando arver, og `flows`\nnavngir gjenbrukbare verktøykjeder. Se\n[referansen for prosjektfiler](/reference/project-file) for det fulle skjemaet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-168@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "4. Run a flow"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "4. Kjør en flyt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-169@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "From anywhere inside the project tree, run a flow by name:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Fra hvor som helst i prosjekttreet, kjør en flyt ved navn:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-16@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Both are the same commands over a different **binding** (where content enters and\nleaves): ad-hoc writes files, while in a project a run commits to the store and\n`kapi merge` materializes the localized files. See **[Modes &\nbindings](/kapi/modes)** for the full model — the source/sink binding diagram, the\ntwo project loops, the portable `.klz` parcel, and when it makes sense to mix."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Begge er de samme kommandoene over en ulik **binding** (hvor innholdet kommer\ninn og går ut): ad hoc skriver filer, mens i et prosjekt skriver en kjøring til\nlageret og `kapi merge` materialiserer de lokaliserte filene. Se **[Moduser og\nbindinger](/kapi/modes)** for hele modellen — diagrammet over\nkilde-/sluk-bindinger, de to prosjektsløyfene, den portable `.klz`-pakken, og\nnår det gir mening å kombinere."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-170@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "kapi discovers the nearest recipe by walking up the directory tree (like git),\nresolves the project's languages and content, and runs the flow. In a project, a\nrun is **process-only** — it commits results to the project store\n(`.kapi/cache/blocks.db`) rather than writing files directly. That keeps repeated\nruns cheap and lets the store accumulate translation memory and overlays as you\nwork."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "kapi oppdager nærmeste oppskrift ved å gå oppover i katalogtreet (som git),\nløser prosjektets språk og innhold, og kjører flyten. I et prosjekt er en kjøring\n**ren prosessering** — den skriver resultatene til prosjektlageret\n(`.kapi/cache/blocks.db`) i stedet for å skrive filer direkte. Det holder\ngjentatte kjøringer billige og lar lageret bygge opp oversettelsesminne og\noverlegg mens du arbeider."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-171@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "5. Merge the files out"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "5. Flett filene ut"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-172@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "When you're ready to materialize the localized files, `merge` writes them to the\ntargets declared in the recipe:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når du er klar til å materialisere de lokaliserte filene, skriver `merge` dem\ntil målene oppgitt i oppskriften:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-173@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "This replays the stored translations onto each source and writes\n`src/locales/fr/*.json`, `src/locales/de/*.json`, and so on — no flags, because\nthe recipe already says where each locale goes."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dette spiller de lagrede oversettelsene tilbake på hver kilde og skriver\n`src/locales/fr/*.json`, `src/locales/de/*.json` og så videre — ingen flagg,\nfordi oppskriften allerede sier hvor hvert språk går."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-174@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Inspect a project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Inspiser et prosjekt"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-175@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The lab below is a project, interactive. Pick a sample, step through a declared\nflow, and watch the recipe, the per-locale state, and the output files update:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Laben under er et prosjekt, interaktivt. Velg et eksempel, gå gjennom en\ndeklarert flyt steg for steg, og se oppskriften, tilstanden per språk og\nutdatafilene oppdatere seg:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-176@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Why project mode"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hvorfor prosjektmodus"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-177@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Project mode trades a one-time `init` for less repetition and more memory:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Prosjektmodus bytter en engangs `init` mot mindre gjentakelse og mer minne:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-178@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Defaults captured once.** Source and target languages, content globs, and\n  flow definitions live in the recipe. You stop passing `--source-lang`,\n  `--target-lang`, and `-i/-o` on every command."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Standardvalg fanget én gang.** Kilde- og målspråk, innholdsglobber og\n  flytdefinisjoner bor i oppskriften. Du slutter å sende `--source-lang`,\n  `--target-lang` og `-i/-o` på hver kommando."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-179@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Translation memory accumulates.** The project store keeps a TM and termbase\n  that every run reads and writes, so each pass recycles the last one's work."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Oversettelsesminnet bygger seg opp.** Prosjektlageret holder et\n  oversettelsesminne og en termbase som hver kjøring leser og skriver, så hver\n  omgang gjenbruker den forriges arbeid."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-17@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "See the [project file reference](/reference/project-file) for the full `.kapi`\nformat."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Se [referansen for prosjektfiler](/reference/project-file) for det\nfullstendige `.kapi`-formatet."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-180@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Git-style discovery.** Run `kapi` from any subdirectory and it finds the\n  project automatically — no `-p` flag, no cwd dance."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Git-aktig oppdagelse.** Kjør `kapi` fra en hvilken som helst underkatalog, og\n  den finner prosjektet automatisk — ingen `-p`-flagg, ingen cwd-dans."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-181@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Portable and shareable.** The recipe is a committed YAML file; a teammate who\n  clones the repository runs the same flows with the same configuration."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Portabel og delbar.** Oppskriften er en innsjekket YAML-fil; en lagkamerat\n  som kloner kodelageret kjører de samme flytene med samme konfigurasjon."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-182@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Ad-hoc runs stay available for one-offs, scripting, and CI — the two are the same\ncommands over a different **binding** (where content enters and leaves). See\n**[Modes & bindings](/kapi/modes)** for the full model."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ad hoc-kjøringer er fortsatt tilgjengelige for engangstilfeller, skripting og CI\n— de to er de samme kommandoene over en ulik **binding** (hvor innholdet kommer\ninn og går ut). Se **[Moduser og bindinger](/kapi/modes)** for hele modellen."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-183@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Next"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Neste"
          }
        ]
      },
