    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-28@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "TM in the loop"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Oversettelsesminnet i sløyfen"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-29@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The two commands that define this workflow are `kapi extract` and\n`kapi merge`. The translation memory participates on both sides:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "De to kommandoene som definerer denne arbeidsflyten er `kapi extract` og\n`kapi merge`. Oversettelsesminnet deltar på begge sider:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-2@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Kapi** reads, translates, and ships content in **any format** — faithfully —\nand verifies it with **checks** (terminology, QA, brand voice) that act like\n**tests for AI output**. It is built on the open-source\n[neokapi framework](/framework/architecture) and comes in two forms that share\nthe same engine, tools, flows, and [`.kapi` projects](/reference/project-file):"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Kapi** leser, oversetter og leverer innhold i **alle formater** — formattro —\nog verifiserer det med **sjekker** (terminologi, kvalitetskontroll,\nmerkevarestemme) som fungerer som **tester for AI-produsert innhold**. Det er\nbygget på det åpne [neokapi-rammeverket](/framework/architecture) og finnes i to\nformer som deler samme motor, verktøy, flyter og\n[`.kapi`-prosjekter](/reference/project-file):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-30@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**TM pre-fill on extract** — every segment is looked up against the\n  project TM before it lands in the XLIFF. Exact matches are pre-filled\n  with `state=\"translated\"`; fuzzy matches above the recipe's\n  `tm.fuzzy_threshold` are pre-filled as fuzzy. The translator's CAT\n  tool shows leverage as a normal TM match."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**TM-forhåndsutfylling ved uttrekk** — hvert segment slås opp mot prosjektets\n  oversettelsesminne før det lander i XLIFF-en. Eksakte treff forhåndsutfylles\n  med `state=\"translated\"`; fuzzy-treff over oppskriftens `tm.fuzzy_threshold`\n  forhåndsutfylles som fuzzy. Oversetterens CAT-verktøy viser gjenbruket som et\n  vanlig TM-treff."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-31@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**TM absorb on merge** — every accepted target segment becomes a new\n  or updated translation unit (TU) in the project TM, carrying\n  provenance (merge batch id, source file path, block content hash,\n  originating XLIFF filename) so a later `kapi tm audit --batch <id>`\n  can trace every TU back to the merge that introduced it."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**TM-absorbering ved fletting** — hvert akseptert målsegment blir en ny eller\n  oppdatert oversettelsesenhet (TU) i prosjektets oversettelsesminne, med\n  proveniens (flettebatch-id, kildefilsti, blokkens innholdshash, opprinnelig\n  XLIFF-filnavn) slik at en senere `kapi tm audit --batch <id>` kan spore hver TU\n  tilbake til flettingen som innførte den."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-32@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "See the round-trip on a bilingual file"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Se rundturen på en tospråklig fil"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-33@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The diagram above is the workflow; the explorer below is the engine that\nmakes it safe. Pick the bilingual XLIFF sample, run it through, and compare\nthe source with the round-tripped output — kapi reads the file into the\ncontent model, the leaf text is replaced, and everything else (structure,\nidentifiers, the skeleton `kapi merge` later rewrites from) comes back\nunchanged. The same reader and writer back `kapi extract` and `kapi merge`,\nrunning here in your browser via WebAssembly."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Diagrammet over er arbeidsflyten; utforskeren under er motoren som gjør den\ntrygg. Velg det tospråklige XLIFF-eksempelet, kjør det gjennom, og sammenlign\nkilden med utdataene fra rundturen — kapi leser filen inn i innholdsmodellen,\nbladteksten byttes ut, og alt annet (struktur, identifikatorer, skjelettet\n`kapi merge` senere skriver om fra) kommer tilbake uendret. Den samme leseren og\nskriveren ligger bak `kapi extract` og `kapi merge`, og kjører her i nettleseren\ndin via WebAssembly."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-34@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Both are on by default. `--no-tm` and `--no-tm-update` disable them\n(e.g. cold-translation workflows or dry-run review)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Begge er på som standard. `--no-tm` og `--no-tm-update` slår dem av\n(f.eks. for arbeidsflyter med kald oversettelse eller gjennomgang som tørrkjøring)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-35@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The .kapi recipe"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
