    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-50@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Common extract options"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Vanlige uttrekksvalg"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-51@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Multi-target in one pass is the default. Omit `--target-lang` to use\nevery locale in `defaults.target_languages`; pass a comma-separated\nsubset to restrict."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flere mål i én omgang er standard. Utelat `--target-lang` for å bruke hvert\nspråk i `defaults.target_languages`; send en kommaseparert delmengde for å\nbegrense."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-52@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "When extraction is redacted (`--redact`, `--redact-rules`, or\n`defaults.redaction` in the recipe), the emitted file carries only\nplaceholders and the originals stay in a local vault; `kapi merge`\nrestores them automatically. See [Redaction](/framework/redaction)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når uttrekket er sladdet (`--redact`, `--redact-rules`, eller\n`defaults.redaction` i oppskriften), bærer den utskrevne filen bare\nplassholdere og originalene blir i et lokalt hvelv; `kapi merge` gjenoppretter\ndem automatisk. Se [Sladding](/framework/redaction)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-53@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Day 2: translator work"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dag 2: oversetterarbeid"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-54@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Out-of-scope for kapi. The translator opens the XLIFF/PO in their CAT\ntool of choice, translates it, and returns it. Kapi is entirely out of\nthe loop during this phase — which is exactly the point. Any bilingual\ntool that speaks XLIFF 2.x works."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Utenfor kapis ansvar. Oversetteren åpner XLIFF-en/PO-en i sitt foretrukne\nCAT-verktøy, oversetter den og returnerer den. Kapi er helt ute av sløyfen i\ndenne fasen — som er nettopp poenget. Ethvert tospråklig verktøy som snakker\nXLIFF 2.x fungerer."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-55@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Day N: merge the return"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dag N: flett inn returen"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-56@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Merge resolves the extraction manifest by reading the batch id from the\nfile's `<note category=\"kapi\" id=\"batch-id\">` — the filename can\nchange during the vendor round-trip and merge still finds the right\nbatch."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flettingen finner uttrekksmanifestet ved å lese batch-id-en fra filens\n`<note category=\"kapi\" id=\"batch-id\">` — filnavnet kan endre seg under\nleverandør-rundturen, og flettingen finner fortsatt riktig batch."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-57@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Multi-file in one pass:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flere filer i én omgang:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-58@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Each returning XLIFF is applied independently. A failure on one\ninput (parse error, missing manifest, stale source) doesn't abort the\nothers — per-file outcomes are reported and the exit code reflects any\nfailure."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hver returnerende XLIFF behandles uavhengig. En feil på én inndatafil\n(parsefeil, manglende manifest, foreldet kilde) avbryter ikke de andre —\nutfallet rapporteres per fil, og avslutningskoden gjenspeiler enhver feil."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-59@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Stale segments"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Foreldede segmenter"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-5@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Because both front-ends run the same engine, a workflow built in one works in\nthe other: the flows and the project file are identical."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Siden begge grensesnittene kjører samme motor, fungerer en arbeidsflyt bygget\ni det ene også i det andre: flytene og prosjektfilen er identiske."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-60@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Merge compares every incoming block's `<source>` against the current\nsource file. If the source text drifted since extract (someone edited\nthe JSON while the XLIFF was out with the translator), that block is\nreported as **stale** and **skipped** — neither applied nor TM-absorbed.\nYou can re-extract and re-translate the drifted portion."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flettingen sammenligner hver innkommende blokks `<source>` med den gjeldende\nkildefilen. Hvis kildeteksten har endret seg siden uttrekket (noen redigerte\nJSON-en mens XLIFF-en var ute hos oversetteren), rapporteres den blokken som\n**foreldet** og **hoppes over** — verken anvendt eller absorbert i\noversettelsesminnet. Du kan trekke ut og oversette den endrede delen på nytt."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-61@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Conflict policy"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Konfliktpolicy"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-62@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "When an on-disk target (or TM TU) already carries a translation for a\nblock, `merge.conflict_policy` picks what happens:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Når et mål på disk (eller en TU i oversettelsesminnet) allerede bærer en\noversettelse for en blokk, velger `merge.conflict_policy` hva som skjer:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-63@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "The same policy applies to TM write-back when a TU for this source already\nhas a translation — never ambiguous, never interactive."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Samme policy gjelder for TM-tilbakeskriving når en TU for denne kilden allerede\nhar en oversettelse — aldri tvetydig, aldri interaktiv."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-64@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Audit: what did this merge contribute?"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Revisjon: hva bidro denne flettingen med?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-65@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Lists every TM entry written or updated by a specific merge with\ntimestamp, source file path, block content hash, and originating\nXLIFF filename — the answer to \"what did this merge do?\" without\nleaving the CLI."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Lister hver TM-oppføring skrevet eller oppdatert av en bestemt fletting, med\ntidsstempel, kildefilsti, blokkens innholdshash og opprinnelig XLIFF-filnavn —\nsvaret på «hva gjorde denne flettingen?» uten å forlate CLI-en."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-66@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "PO (gettext) alternative"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "PO-alternativet (gettext)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-67@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Same flow, different exchange format:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Samme flyt, annet utvekslingsformat:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-68@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "PO output carries kapi's bookkeeping as extracted comments:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "PO-utdata bærer kapis bokføring som uttrukne kommentarer:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-69@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "File-level (on the header entry): `#. kapi-batch:`,\n  `#. kapi-source-file:`, `#. kapi-source-hash:`"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "På filnivå (på hodeoppføringen): `#. kapi-batch:`,\n  `#. kapi-source-file:`, `#. kapi-source-hash:`"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-6@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Extract content from a file, translate it, run checks, and write it back in the\nsame format — a full bilingual round-trip from the terminal:"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Trekk ut innhold fra en fil, oversett det, kjør sjekker og skriv det tilbake\ni samme format — en fullstendig tospråklig rundtur fra terminalen:"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-70@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Per-entry: `#. kapi-block: <block-id>` for merge correlation"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Per oppføring: `#. kapi-block: <block-id>` for flettekorrelasjon"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-71@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "`#, fuzzy` on entries pre-filled from fuzzy TM matches"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "`#, fuzzy` på oppføringer forhåndsutfylt fra fuzzy TM-treff"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-72@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "A single `kapi merge -i` invocation can mix XLIFF and PO inputs from\nthe same batch — useful when different vendors ship in different\nformats."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Ett enkelt `kapi merge -i`-kall kan blande XLIFF- og PO-inndata fra samme\nbatch — nyttig når ulike leverandører leverer i ulike formater."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-73@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": ":::note\nPO output is one entry per block (matches the segmentation-off case).\nEnabling `defaults.segmentation.source: true` together with\n`--format po` errors early; emit XLIFF for projects that rely on\nsentence-level segmentation.\n:::"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": ":::note\nPO-utdata er én oppføring per blokk (tilsvarer tilfellet med segmentering av).\nÅ slå på `defaults.segmentation.source: true` sammen med `--format po` feiler\ntidlig; skriv ut XLIFF for prosjekter som er avhengige av segmentering på\nsetningsnivå.\n:::"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-74@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "What stays in the project"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Hva som blir i prosjektet"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-75@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "XLIFF and PO carry exactly one chosen target per locale, the source runs\nand inline codes, and — with the captured skeleton — enough to rebuild the\noriginal file byte-for-byte. Everything else in kapi's content model is\n**deliberately not** projected into the bilingual file; it stays in project\nstate (the translation memory, termbase, and stand-off overlays):"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "XLIFF og PO bærer nøyaktig ett valgt mål per språk, kildens runs og\ninline-kodene, og — med det fangede skjelettet — nok til å gjenoppbygge\noriginalfilen byte for byte. Alt annet i kapis innholdsmodell projiseres\n**bevisst ikke** inn i den tospråklige filen; det blir i prosjekttilstanden\n(oversettelsesminnet, termbasen og de frittstående overleggene):"
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-76@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Stand-off overlays** — terminology, entity, and QA annotations anchored\n  to run ranges."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Frittstående overlegg** — terminologi-, entitets- og QA-annotasjoner forankret\n  til run-områder."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-77@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Tone / channel variants** — alternate targets keyed by more than locale."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Tone-/kanalvarianter** — alternative mål nøklet på mer enn språkkode."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-78@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "**Provenance and status** — where each target came from (TM pre-fill, a\n  specific merge batch, an MT or AI tool) and its review state."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "**Proveniens og status** — hvor hvert mål kom fra (TM-forhåndsutfylling, en\n  bestemt flettebatch, et MT- eller AI-verktøy) og dets gjennomgangsstatus."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-1548425fb44d29f8-1781164979411269788"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "docs-nb.tmx:tu-79@tmx-1548425f",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "This is by design: the bilingual file is the lean, tool-neutral handoff,\nand the project is the system of record. It is also why merge needs the\nsame project the extract ran in — the skeleton and manifest that make the\nround-trip byte-exact live there, not in the file the translator returns."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Dette er tilsiktet: den tospråklige filen er den slanke, verktøynøytrale\noverleveringen, og prosjektet er den autoritative kilden. Det er også derfor\nflettingen trenger det samme prosjektet uttrekket kjørte i — skjelettet og\nmanifestet som gjør rundturen byte-eksakt bor der, ikke i filen oversetteren\nreturnerer."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "docs-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
